videos.description: Aaron Holiday drives through traffic, makes a hesitation move and gets the layup to put UCLA in the lead early.
videos.headline: UCLA's Holiday hesitates for lay-in

videos.description: Aaron Holiday gets a speedy layup to put the Bruins on a 12-0 run in the first half.
videos.headline: Holiday lay-in part of UCLA 12-0 run

videos.description: John Edgar Jr. gets a pass to Max Hazzard who sinks a 3-pointer, giving him 14 points at the beginning of the second half.
videos.headline: Hazzard stays hot for UC Irvine

videos.description: Kris Wilkes finds his way around the defender to get a lay-in while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Wilkes makes tough layup for UCLA
